<item>
            <title>[CXF-8354] Logs not redirecting to Log4J</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-8354</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Log4jLogger&lt;/tt&gt; was removed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-8264&quot; title=&quot;Remove Log4J 1.x dependencies&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CXF-8264&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CXF-8264&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but &lt;tt&gt;LogUtils&lt;/tt&gt; is still trying to instantiate it when SLF4J has a binding for Log4J or JCL-&amp;gt;Log4J.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As a result, when both slf4j and log4j-slf4j-impl are in the classpath, CXF still sends logs to JUL.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;LogUtils&lt;/tt&gt; should always use &lt;tt&gt;Slf4jLogger&lt;/tt&gt; instead.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will submit a PR on GitHub to fix this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
